{/* Hero Section */}

Dean Roy For Vermont

Dean Roy is running to become the first governor under the age of 18 and reduce the affordability crisis.

{/* Quote Section */}
"This isn't about me. This is about making a more affordable Vermont for all of us." - Dean Roy
{/* Meet Dean Roy Section */}

Meet Dean Roy

Dean Roy is a student at Stowe Middle School and a member of the Freedom and Unity party. Born and raised in Vermont, Roy has developed ties to his community and city. His plans include consolidating school districts, taxing large corporations and short-term rentals, strengthening ties with Canada and the EU, and keeping Vermont free from all those who try to harm it. If elected, Roy would be the youngest Governor in the history of America.

{/* Get Involved Section */}

GET INVOLVED

Join the many people involved in our path to victory.

Sign up below, and we'll give you an email once we begin official campaigning.
